title: [Cyraeni's House, Entry]
description: A large bay window is placed at the front end of the extended hallway, offsetting the dark hardwood floors with a shock of exposed outdoor greenery.  Milky beeswax candles sit in cobalt porcelain sconces that line the whitewashed walls.
